菲律賓的電視廣播站雖然也使用菲律賓時間，但是總有一些小的誤差。2011年9月科學和技術部（Department of Science and Technology）提議統一全國各地的時間。因此天文服務單位便安裝了銣[[原子鐘|原子鐘]]以達成此目的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/lifestyle/09/26/11/juan-time-filipino-time-redefined |title=Juan Time: Filipino time redefined {{!}} ABS-CBN News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-04-15 |archive-date=2014-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140124070609/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/lifestyle/09/26/11/juan-time-filipino-time-redefined |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年5月15日，菲律賓總統[[貝尼格諾·阿基諾三世|貝尼格諾·阿基諾三世]]簽署第10535號法案，即2013年菲律賓標準時間法案（Philippine Standard Time Act of 2013）完成了時令改革的最後一步。2013年6月1日所有政府部門和媒體網絡均被要求使用規定的菲律賓標準時間。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/310076/scitech/technology/phl-standard-time-to-counter-filipino-time-starting-june-1 |title=PHL Standard Time to counter 'Filipino time' starting June 1 {{!}} SciTech {{!}} GMA News Online<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-04-15 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220194349/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/310076/scitech/technology/phl-standard-time-to-counter-filipino-time-starting-june-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/video/nation/05/24/13/are-you-philippine-standard-time |title=Are you on Philippine Standard Time? {{!}} ABS-CBN News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-04-15 |archive-date=2014-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140124065056/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/video/nation/05/24/13/are-you-philippine-standard-time |dead-url=no }}</ref>

